OL,3,CHospital orders inquiry after
OL,4,Canaesthetist jailed for child abuse
OL,5,Cimages
OL,7,FA hospital in Devon has ordered an
OL,8,Fexternal review after a senior
OL,9,Fanaesthetist was jailed for
OL,10,Fdownloading 14,000 images of child
OL,11,Fabuse.
OL,13,FDr Alexander Grice worked at the Royal
OL,14,FDevon and Exeter Hospital (RD&E) and
OL,15,Fwas sentenced at Exeter Crown Court
OL,16,Flast on Friday 8 March after police
OL,17,Ffound thousands of illegal photos on
OL,18,Fhis iPhone and computer.
