OL,8,Fafter Grice, who has since changed his
OL,9,Fsurname to Knight, was seen watching
OL,10,Fadult pornography on his phone while
OL,11,Fsupervising an operation in May 2022.
OL,13,FThe video he was watching showed a
OL,14,Fpartially naked woman on an operating
OL,15,Ftable.
