OL,7,FPolice found that some of the images
OL,8,Fof child abuse Grice had on his phone
OL,9,Fwere also in hospital settings, but
OL,10,Fthey found these had been downloaded
OL,11,Ffrom the internet rather than created
OL,12,Fby him.
OL,14,FBut it was not the first time Grice
OL,15,Fhad been in trouble - the 54-year-old
OL,16,Fwas prosecuted in 2017 in France for
OL,17,Fvoyeurism after he was caught secretly
OL,18,Ffilming in a shower block at a
OL,19,Fcampsite.
