OL,7,FThe General Medical Council and the
OL,8,FRD&E decided Grice had been
OL,9,Fexperiencing poor mental health at the
OL,10,Ftime and allowed him to continue
OL,11,Fworking in Devon following treatment.
OL,13,FRD&E NHS Trust: 'There is no
OL,14,Fsuggestion any crimes were committed
OL,15,Fat the Trust'
OL,17,FDr Knight has been interim suspended
OL,18,Fsince July 2022, pending the
OL,19,Fconclusion of a full GMC
OL,20,Finvestigation, meaning he has been
OL,21,Fprevented from treating patients.
