OL,7,FThe hospital has now ordered an
OL,8,Fexternal review and asked any patients
OL,9,Fwho are worried to contact a helpline
OL,10,Fthey have set up.
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "We are shocked
OL,13,Fand saddened by the nature of these
OL,14,Fcrimes and our thoughts are with those
OL,15,Faffected.
OL,17,F"Of the crimes Alexander Knight was
OL,18,Fcharged with, there is no suggestion
OL,19,Fany were committed on Trust premises
OL,20,For involved any of the Trust's
OL,21,Fpatients.
