OL,7,F"Alexander Knight was excluded as soon
OL,8,Fas he was arrested and never returned
OL,9,Fto work at the Trust.
OL,11,F"Following his arrest in June 2022 all
OL,12,Fappropriate processes were followed
OL,13,Fand we continue to work closely with
OL,14,FDevon & Cornwall Police and the GMC.
OL,16,F"In line with our commitment to a just
OL,17,Fand learning culture, we have also
OL,18,Fcommissioned an external review to
OL,19,Fconsider whether there is anything we
OL,20,Fcan learn from this.
