OL,7,F"We understand that this news may be
OL,8,Fvery distressing to read and if the
OL,9,Fpublic would like to talk and share
OL,10,Fany concerns they can contact our
OL,11,Fhelpline on 01271 322334.
OL,13,F"The helpline is open Monday to Friday
OL,14,F9.30 ` 4pm."
OL,16,FGrice, of East Street, Chulmleigh, and
OL,17,Fformerly of Poughill, Crediton,
OL,18,Fadmitted three counts of making, by
OL,19,Fdownloading, indecent images of
OL,20,Fchildren, and possession of prohibited
OL,21,Fand extreme images.
