OL,7,FPolice found more than 14,000 images
OL,8,For movies on his phone or hard drive,
OL,9,Fof which 3,423, were in the worst
OL,10,Fcategory, effectively showing child
OL,11,Frape. Another 2,822 showed non-
OL,12,Fpenetrative abuse, and 8,890 showed
OL,13,Fnaked or partially naked children.
OL,15,FHe has changed his surname to Knight
OL,16,Fsince being charged with these
OL,17,Foffences and appeared at Exeter Crown
OL,18,FCourt under his new name.
