OL,7,FHe was jailed for a year and eight
OL,8,Fmonths by Judge David Evans, who also
OL,9,Fput him on the sex offenders register
OL,10,Fand made him subject to an order which
OL,11,Fenables the police to monitor his use
OL,12,Fof the internet, both for ten years.
OL,14,FDuring the hearing, the court was told
OL,15,FGrice used a Virtual Private Network
OL,16,Fto conceal his identity and used an
OL,17,FOnion router to access chat rooms on
OL,18,Fthe dark web where he accessed the
OL,19,Fmaterial.
