OL,7,FHe was sacked by the hospital after an
OL,8,Finvestigation, his wife has divorced
OL,9,Fhim and he has been shunned by his
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,FMr Nick Wragg, defending, said Grice
OL,13,Fwas suffering from serious mental
OL,14,Fhealth issues when he committed the
OL,15,Foffences.
