OL,7,FHe said: "It has been a catastrophic
OL,8,Ffall from grace. He had been a very
OL,9,Fsuccessful man and the impact on him
OL,10,Fhas been very great. He attempted
OL,11,Fsuicide after his arrest but has since
OL,12,Fprivately funded 42 sessions with a
OL,13,Fpsychotherapist."
OL,15,FHe said his client now understands the
OL,16,Fharm done to the children who were
OL,17,Fabused to create the material.
