OL,7,FIn passing sentence, Judge Evans told
OL,8,FGrice: "There was deliberate searching
OL,9,Ffor such imagery and evidence that you
OL,10,Fwere an avid user of chat rooms.
OL,12,F"Some of the victims were unconscious
OL,13,For drugged. Many of the children
OL,14,Fdepicted being raped were very young
OL,15,Fand vulnerable and some showed
OL,16,Fdiscernible pain or distress.
OL,18,F"You are undoubtedly a person with
OL,19,Fpersonal qualities and achievements.
OL,20,FYou have lost your job, your career,
OL,21,Fyour family and your good name."
